Class BOBaseUser

java.lang.Object
  de.htwg_konstanz.ebus.framework.wholesaler.api.bo.BOBaseUser
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBOUser
Direct Known Subclasses:
BOUserCustomer, BOUserInternal, BOUserSupplier
public abstract class BOBaseUser
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBOUser

The business object BOBaseUser represents the base class for all user objects. The object provides common user attributes like name, login, address or email.

The base class is defined as an abstract class, so you can't instantiate them. Use the derived classes "BOUserInternal", "BOUserSupplier" and "BOUserCustomer" instead.
